&ldquo;In the beginning God created the heaven and the earth. And the earth was without form, and void; and darkness was upon the face of the deep. And the Spirit of God moved upon the face of the waters. And God said, &lsquo;Let there be light&rsquo;: and there was light. And God saw the light that it was good…&rdquo;
